<% title 'Your safety' %>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    <%= step_header %>
    <p class="app__section_heading">Safety concerns</p>
    <h1 class="app__heading heading-xlarge gv-u-heading-xxlarge">Your safety</h1>

    <div class=" govuk-govspeak gv-s-prose">
      <p>The court needs to know if you have experienced, or are at risk of experiencing, any form of domestic violence or abuse.</p>
      <p>The following questions will ask whether you have experienced, or are at risk of experiencing, any form of harm.</p>
      <p>Find out about the
        <a href="https://www.refuge.org.uk/get-help-now/help-for-women/recognising-abuse/" target="external_link" rel="external">signs
          of domestic violence or abuse</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="xform-group form-submit">
      <%= link_to 'Continue', edit_steps_abuse_concerns_question_path(subject: AbuseSubject::APPLICANT), class: 'button', role: 'button' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
